SQL Grammar

stmt_block:

stmt_block
         ::= stmt_list

no references


stmt_list:

stmt_list
         ::= stmt ( ';' stmt )*

referenced by:

  • stmt_block


stmt:

stmt     ::= alter_table_stmt
           | create_stmt
           | delete_stmt
           | drop_stmt
           | explain_stmt
           | grant_stmt
           | insert_stmt
           | rename_stmt
           | revoke_stmt
           | select_stmt
           | set_stmt
           | show_stmt
           | transaction_stmt
           | truncate_stmt
           | update_stmt
           |

referenced by:

  • stmt_list


alter_table_stmt:

alter_table_stmt
         ::= 'ALTER' 'TABLE' relation_expr alter_table_cmds
           | 'ALTER' 'TABLE' 'IF' 'EXISTS' relation_expr alter_table_cmds

referenced by:

  • stmt


create_stmt:

create_stmt
         ::= create_database_stmt
           | create_index_stmt
           | create_table_stmt

referenced by:

  • stmt


delete_stmt:

delete_stmt
         ::= 'DELETE' 'FROM' relation_expr_opt_alias where_clause returning_clause

referenced by:

  • explainable_stmt
  • stmt


drop_stmt:

drop_stmt
         ::= 'DROP' 'DATABASE' name
           | 'DROP' 'DATABASE' 'IF' 'EXISTS' name
           | 'DROP' 'INDEX' qualified_name_list
           | 'DROP' 'INDEX' 'IF' 'EXISTS' qualified_name_list
           | 'DROP' 'TABLE' any_name_list
           | 'DROP' 'TABLE' 'IF' 'EXISTS' any_name_list

referenced by:

  • stmt


explain_stmt:

explain_stmt
         ::= 'EXPLAIN' explainable_stmt
           | 'EXPLAIN' '(' explain_option_list ')' explainable_stmt

referenced by:

  • stmt


grant_stmt:

grant_stmt
         ::= 'GRANT' privileges 'ON' privilege_target 'TO' grantee_list

referenced by:

  • stmt


insert_stmt:

insert_stmt
         ::= 'INSERT' 'INTO' insert_target insert_rest returning_clause

referenced by:

  • explainable_stmt
  • stmt


rename_stmt:

rename_stmt
         ::= 'ALTER' 'DATABASE' name 'RENAME' 'TO' name
           | 'ALTER' 'TABLE' relation_expr 'RENAME' 'TO' qualified_name
           | 'ALTER' 'TABLE' 'IF' 'EXISTS' relation_expr 'RENAME' 'TO' qualified_name
           | 'ALTER' 'INDEX' qualified_name 'RENAME' 'TO' name
           | 'ALTER' 'INDEX' 'IF' 'EXISTS' qualified_name 'RENAME' 'TO' name
           | 'ALTER' 'TABLE' relation_expr 'RENAME' opt_column name 'TO' name
           | 'ALTER' 'TABLE' 'IF' 'EXISTS' relation_expr 'RENAME' opt_column name 'TO' name
           | 'ALTER' 'TABLE' relation_expr 'RENAME' 'CONSTRAINT' name 'TO' name
           | 'ALTER' 'TABLE' 'IF' 'EXISTS' relation_expr 'RENAME' 'CONSTRAINT' name 'TO' name

referenced by:

  • stmt

revoke_stmt

set_stmt:

set_stmt ::= 'SET' set_rest
           | 'SET' 'LOCAL' set_rest

show_stmt:

show_stmt
         ::= 'SHOW' 'IDENT'
           | 'SHOW' 'DATABASE'
           | 'SHOW' 'COLUMNS' 'FROM' var_name
           | 'SHOW' 'DATABASES'
           | 'SHOW' 'GRANTS' on_privilege_target_clause for_grantee_clause

           | 'SHOW' 'TABLES' opt_from_var_name_clause
           | 'SHOW' 'TIME' 'ZONE'
           | 'SHOW' 'TRANSACTION' 'ISOLATION' 'LEVEL'

           | 'SHOW' 'ALL'

           | 'ROLLBACK' opt_transaction
